From: STGR Browser Team <dev@stgr-browser.dev>
Date: Tue, 2 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: Tab preview with actual page screenshots via PageThumbs capture

Replaces the text-only tab preview (title + URL) with a real page
screenshot captured from the tab's browser content.

Uses PageThumbs API as primary capture method, with canvas.drawWindow
fallback. Implements LRU thumbnail cache (20 entries, 30s TTL) to
avoid re-capturing recently-viewed tabs. Cache is invalidated on
tab navigation and tab close. Progress listener is properly cleaned
up on window destroy.

